{"id": 1673, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你都会和什么人讨论严肃话题？", "description": "政治啊，人生啊，理想啊……现在你其实都会主动跟谁讨论呢？（题图来自：Steve Buissinne）", "record_count": 2160, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201705081414580OVTCYmGhP9oFuLe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-24T03:00:10Z", "options": [{"id": 206848, "content": "没有讲不讲，只不过没人听", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024993}, {"id": 207104, "content": "除自己，找不到他人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024075}, {"id": 208128, "content": "人之一生，怎么才能算活过。平凡人如我，有天突然消失，那这世界上根本没有我的痕迹，就好像我从来没来过一样。想想都觉得不甘。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041780}, {"id": 206849, "content": "跟我哥会讨论一些严肃的话题，比如工作赚钱等等", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932097}, {"id": 207105, "content": "没有人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039574}, {"id": 208129, "content": "人活过的痕迹在哪里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041780}, {"id": 207106, "content": "认识的几乎没人关注这些，只有自己与自己对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973371}, {"id": 206851, "content": "曾经和女朋友谈过严肃的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932097}, {"id": 207107, "content": "和同样对严肃话题感兴趣的人谈，因为可以得到反馈。而不是你说一堆，对方只回一句“好吧”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036424}, {"id": 207108, "content": "很那些生活质量不错的人聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 995495}, {"id": 206853, "content": "Brook", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1036258}, {"id": 207109, "content": "父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599378}, {"id": 214533, "content": "没有人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679333}, {"id": 207110, "content": "和关系较好的谈论历史", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039593}, {"id": 208390, "content": "当下电视剧的各种肉类食品", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042198}, {"id": 215302, "content": "对过去的自己！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061055}, {"id": 206855, "content": "和有共同兴趣的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339377}, {"id": 207367, "content": "苦思冥想", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983351}, {"id": 207879, "content": "自己的心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041844}, {"id": 208135, "content": "什么叫严肃的话题(눈‸눈)能跟别人说的话题都不严肃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042769}, {"id": 206856, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573723}, {"id": 207368, "content": "反正不是男朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040329}, {"id": 208392, "content": "能我安安静静坐下来一起抽烟的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042198}, {"id": 228360, "content": "知音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 589122}, {"id": 207369, "content": "最近的是前男友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040326}, {"id": 207114, "content": "舍友，特别要好的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 207115, "content": "结婚8年的老公。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746414}, {"id": 207371, "content": "那要看问题严肃到什么程度\n以这种程度可以分级，如果\n是最高级的，我相信只有认\n为最亲密的朋友或者我爱的\n父母认真谈。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040331}, {"id": 214283, "content": "自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058389}, {"id": 207116, "content": "和一个有思想的，很好的朋友谈，一些世界观，比较需要成熟思考的问题。可惜现在不能和她在一个学校了，于是几乎没人谈了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037992}, {"id": 207884, "content": "从初中一直到研究生的挚友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 208908, "content": "室友呀父母呀还有专门的领导力论坛大会之类的，愿意或者可以聊这些平时也有思考的人。就是指很单纯的讲事实，而不是为了装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001890}, {"id": 206861, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/201705241443530JpLhfKQ1ymqgnM2", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573723}, {"id": 207117, "content": "日记本？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031798}, {"id": 208141, "content": "有思想的实诚人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042166}, {"id": 208910, "content": "我有第二人格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1023830}, {"id": 207119, "content": "深夜 和朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 917724}, {"id": 207375, "content": "好像跟男孩子讨论严肃话题多一点，跟女生们总是喜欢聊八卦聊爱豆聊脑洞！不是说女生不深刻，是因为没法跟男生聊爱豆啊！他们get不到点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034967}, {"id": 207122, "content": "一些自己行业的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263648}, {"id": 208914, "content": "好兄弟或者好姐妹", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980278}, {"id": 207123, "content": "自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029437}, {"id": 209427, "content": "刚认识的朋友 实在话和很熟的人反倒不会谈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047203}, {"id": 209939, "content": "感性的同桌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048303}, {"id": 207124, "content": "Maybe 老师", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984869}, {"id": 207892, "content": "自己 和可以直接说实话的说真话的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018761}, {"id": 206869, "content": "软件...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 626648}, {"id": 207125, "content": "老爸和闺蜜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970529}, {"id": 206870, "content": "我还是喜欢跟我爸讨论这些问题~不知道为什么~就是感觉自己的爸爸是万能的~", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953473}, {"id": 207126, "content": "我老姐，不然就是Nobody cares..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1033689}, {"id": 207894, "content": "这些问题呀，当然是和李亚澜了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041948}]}